rComments: Really good teacher.  Very clear with good lecture slides.  Puts resources online and is very helpful.  Minor gripes:  notes don't come online for us to use for class soon enough, homework not announced as often as I would like.

Amy is a great teacher.  For her first year teaching, she really packs a punch when it comes to understanding material.  Her only downfall is that sometimes I find myself only paying attention to her saying 'um' every other sentence.  But I'm being super picky.  She is superb!
fabulous! very clear and fun. very personal..and personable for that matter. i learned a lot in this class and would recommend it to anyone
Amy is so nice! She does a really good job explaining and makes examples fun, and I actually learned something from this class.
